WEBVTT

00:15:28.960 --> 00:15:31.280
changed federal hate crimes policy.

00:15:32.000 --> 00:15:36.776
The choice to love our opponents
is moral and pragmatic,

00:15:36.800 --> 00:15:42.336
and it opens up the previously
unimaginable possibility

00:15:42.360 --> 00:15:43.760
of reconciliation.

00:15:47.800 --> 00:15:49.000
But remember ...

00:15:50.320 --> 00:15:53.160
it took 15 years to make that phone call.

00:15:54.760 --> 00:15:59.840
I had to tend to my own rage
and grief first.